<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - Leafora</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2E2E2E;
            background: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .main-content {
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        /* Page Header */
        .page-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B6F47 0%, #705836 100%);
            padding: 100px 0 80px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .page-header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;
        }

        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.4s backwards;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            opacity: 0.9;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .breadcrumb i {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* Contact Info Cards */
        .contact-info-section {
            padding: 80px 0 40px;
            background: #F5F1EB;
        }

        .contact-info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .contact-info-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .contact-info-card:hover {
            border-color: #8B6F47;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.15);
        }

        .contact-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B6F47 0%, #705836 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .contact-icon i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .contact-info-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #2E2E2E;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .contact-info-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6B6B6B;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .contact-info-card a {
            color: #8B6F47;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-info-card a:hover {
            color: #705836;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Why Contact Us Section */
        .why-contact-section {
            padding: 40px 0 80px;
            background: #F5F1EB;
        }

        .why-contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .why-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .why-card:hover {
            border-color: #8B6F47;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.15);
        }

        .why-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B6F47 0%, #705836 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .why-icon i {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .why-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #2E2E2E;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .why-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6B6B6B;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Map Section */
        .map-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: white;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2E2E2E;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .section-header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #6B6B6B;
        }

        .map-container {
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 450px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .map-container iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        /* FAQ Section */
        .faq-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: #F5F1EB;
        }

        .faq-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .faq-item {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-item:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .faq-item h4 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #2E2E2E;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .faq-item h4 i {
            color: #8B6F47;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-item p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #6B6B6B;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .contact-info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .why-contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .faq-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-content {
                margin-top: 70px;
            }

            .page-header {
                padding: 80px 0 60px;
            }

            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .page-header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .form-text h2,
            .section-header h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .map-container {
                height: 350px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../admin/partials/user/header') %>

    <div class="main-content">
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <section class="page-header">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="page-header-content">
                    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
                    <p>We'd love to hear from you. Get in touch with our team</p>
                    <div class="breadcrumb">
                        <a href="/">Home</a>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                        <span>Contact</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Info Cards -->
        <section class="contact-info-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="contact-info-grid">
                    <div class="contact-info-card">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Visit Us</h3>
                        <p>
                            123 Book Street, Literary District<br>
                            Kozhikode, Kerala 673001<br>
                            India
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-info-card">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Call Us</h3>
                        <p>
                            <a href="tel:+919876543210">+91 98765 43210</a><br>
                            <a href="tel:+914952345678">+91 495 234 5678</a><br>
                            Mon-Sat: 9AM - 8PM
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-info-card">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Email Us</h3>
                        <p>
                            <a href="mailto:support@leafora.com">support@leafora.com</a><br>
                            <a href="mailto:info@leafora.com">info@leafora.com</a><br>
                            We reply within 24 hours
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Contact Us Section -->
        <section class="why-contact-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Why Contact Us?</h2>
                    <p>We're here to help with all your book-related needs</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-contact-grid">
                    <div class="why-card">
                        <div class="why-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Customer Support</h3>
                        <p>Get help with orders, shipping, returns, or any questions about our products and services.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-card">
                        <div class="why-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Book Recommendations</h3>
                        <p>Looking for your next great read? Our team can help you discover books based on your interests.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-card">
                        <div class="why-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Business Inquiries</h3>
                        <p>Interested in partnerships, bulk orders, or collaboration? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-card">
                        <div class="why-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Feedback & Suggestions</h3>
                        <p>Your feedback helps us improve. Share your thoughts and suggestions with us.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Map Section -->
        <section class="map-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Find Us on Map</h2>
                    <p>Visit our store and explore our collection in person</p>
                </div>
                <div class="map-container">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3913.0799812842705!2d75.77158931478673!3d11.258753291997807!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3ba65bfa499e725f%3A0x1f6d7de59c6be58d!2sKozhikode%2C%20Kerala!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1234567890123!5m2!1sen!2sin"
                        allowfullscreen=""
                        loading="lazy"
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                    </iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <section class="faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <p>Quick answers to common questions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> What are your business hours?</h4>
                        <p>We're open Monday to Saturday from 9:00 AM to 8:00 PM. Closed on Sundays and public holidays.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Do you offer international shipping?</h4>
                        <p>Yes! We ship to most countries worldwide. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by location.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> What is your return policy?</h4>
                        <p>We offer a 30-day return policy on most items. Books must be in original condition with no markings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Can I pre-order upcoming releases?</h4>
                        <p>Absolutely! We offer pre-orders for upcoming releases. You'll be charged when the book ships.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <%- include('../admin/partials/user/footer') %>

    <script>
        // Smooth scroll effect for navbar
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const navbar = document.getElementById('navbar');
            if (navbar && window.scrollY > 50) {
                navbar.style.boxShadow = '0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)';
            } else if (navbar) {
                navbar.style.boxShadow = '0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)';
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>